### Healthcheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### USDC transfers — raw format (default)
GET {{baseUrl}}/usdc/transfers/20000000

### USDC transfers — human format
GET {{baseUrl}}/usdc/transfers/20000000?format=human

### USDC transfers — invalid block number (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/usdc/transfers/abc

### USDC transfers — invalid format param (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/usdc/transfers/20000000?format=invalid
